sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Alice
    participant B as Bob
    participant C as Carol
    A->>B: Login
    loop Retry up to 3 times
        B->>C: Validate credentials
        C-->>B: Validation result
    end
    alt User found
        B-->>A: Welcome
    else User not found
        B-->>A: Access denied
    end
    par Notify services
        A->>B: Log event
    and
        A->>C: Send email
    end
    break On exception
        B-->>A: Error
    end
    A->>B: Done
